Class DeliveryTour

java.lang.Object
com.pld.agile.model.entity.DeliveryTour
public class DeliveryTour extends Object
The DeliveryTour class represents a delivery tour for a courier. It contains information about the courier, the start and end times of the tour, the list of delivery requests, the route, and the arrival times at each intersection.

  • Constructor Details

    • DeliveryTour

      public DeliveryTour(Courier courier, LocalTime endTime, List<DeliveryRequest> deliveryRequests, List<Intersection> route, Map<Intersection,LocalTime> arrivalTimes)
      Constructs a new DeliveryTour with the specified courier, end time, delivery requests, route, and arrival times. The start time is set to 8:00 AM by default.
      Parameters:
      courier - the Courier assigned to the tour
      endTime - the time at which the tour is expected to end
      deliveryRequests - the list of DeliveryRequest objects for this tour
      route - the list of Section objects representing the route
      arrivalTimes - the map of Intersection to LocalTime, representing the arrival times at each intersection
